    <h>sgoil</h>
    <p><g>sgoil</g>
        <en>school</en> is a feminine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>sgoil</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>sgoil</m> – nominative/dative singular</li>
                <li><m>sgoile</m> – genitive singular</li>
                <li><m>sgoiltean</m> – nominative/dative/genitive plural</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="definiteness">
            <h>definiteness</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>indefinite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>sgoil</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>sgoil</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – dorus <m>sgoile</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>sgoiltean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>sgoiltean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – dorsan <m>sgoiltean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>definite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>an sgoil</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>an sgoil</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – dorus <m>na sgoile</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na sgoiltean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>na sgoiltean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – dorsan <m>nan sgoiltean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
